    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements for Class II device at medium model influence. CFD predictions of relative hemolysis index demonstrate 4.2% normalised error against bench measurements across the full COU operating envelope. Acceptance criterion RH < 1 satisfied at all operating points. Credibility assessment supports use of CFD model for worst-case hemolysis identification in the defined COU.",
